creator: VoiceFive, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
VPN technology prevents unwanted eyes from seeing what you are doing on your phone. This is especially helpful if you use your phone on public Wi-Fi hotspots like those found at coffee shops, hotels, parks and other locations. Using public Wi-Fi without a VPN makes your phone vulnerable to hackers who could compromise your security by stealing your passwords, banking information, and even your identity.

No VPN Limits or In-App Advertising
Most VPNs cap the amount of data you can use or show you ads in the app, which impacts your experience. MyMobileSecure’s VPN is always on and has no usage limits, no ads, and unlimited bandwidth at no cost to you.

Benefits of MyMobileSecure VPN
🕵️ Helps prevent hacking. MyMobileSecure uses advanced VPN technology to scramble your network traffic which helps to make it indecipherable to hackers.

🔑Unlocks your entertainment. Binge on your favorite shows while travelling. MyMobileSecure routes your connection back to your home country letting you access home content while abroad.

🔐 Secures your information. MyMobileSecure helps to keep the personal information you send and receive private wherever you want to log on, even when you’re connected to a questionable public Wi-Fi hotspot.

💡 Easy. MyMobileSecure is always on. Simply flip a switch once and forget about it.

There is no cost to download and you can uninstall at any time. So, if in doubt, take us for a test drive!

Improve the Mobile Web for Everyone
MyMobileSecure is made available at no cost for members of the MobileXpression research community by comScore, one of the world’s largest research organizations. Sign up is easy and there is no cost to join. We can provide these benefits because we make our money by helping trusted companies understand how consumers use their mobile devices. The data collected by comScore is routinely quoted by major media such as The New York Times®, the Wall Street Journal® and CNN® and is trusted by many Fortune 500® companies to improve their online offers.

To make this possible we will require that you give us permission to monitor and collect data about your mobile browsing, app use, video streaming purchasing behavior (including secure sessions) and call and message frequency.

MyMobileSecure does not support the use of our VPN for illegally sharing copyrighted content. Users found to violate this policy will have their account terminated.

For full details on our privacy practices relating to the collection, use, and disclosure of information, we encourage you to read our Privacy Policy and Terms of Service.

Please note that VPN services like MyMobileSecure are not able to detect or prevent viruses. We recommend that you use a reliable antivirus program alongside MyMobileSecure.
